\n包吃，饭堂好吃</p>\n<p>缺点：\n可能技术成长有限\n国企工作不能出国，各种受限\n不喜欢一眼望到头的生活</p>\n<p>三. 个人考虑：\n211 硕应届生，计算机视觉方向\n本来打算申日本的博士，后面凉了，所以仓促准备秋招，拿到这两个 Offer\n但是后面还是想去读海外博，拿永居，作为一个工作的国家\n和女朋友关系很好，不是很想分开</p>\n<p>感谢各位的建议，个人实在考虑太多</p>\n","last_modified":1685068830,"replies":81,"id":943104},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":56127,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181","stars":8402,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":357553,"username":"miv","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/miv","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d59c/d7bf/357553_mini.png?m=1681841515","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d59c/d7bf/357553_normal.png?m=1681841515","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d59c/d7bf/357553_large.png?m=1681841515","created":1540177705,"last_modified":1681841515},"last_reply_by":"ivslyyy","last_touched":1685114823,"title":"做一个调研，如果有人给你外包单子，你愿意给中间人多少利润？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/943133","created":1685072200,"deleted":0,"content":"比如：有一个人介绍一个单子 1w 元，你接了，你的成本是 5k ，利润 5k 。类似的，你愿意给中间人一部分利润吗？","content_rendered":"<p>比如：有一个人介绍一个单子 1w 元，你接了，你的成本是 5k ，利润 5k 。类似的，你愿意给中间人一部分利润吗？</p>\n","last_modified":1685072200,"replies":78,"id":943133},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":203838,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avata